FBIS4-40296 "drsov116_a_94041" FBIS-SOV-94-116 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Fishermen, PRC Border Guards Clash on Argun River Fishermen, PRC Border Guards Clash on Argun River LD1606112994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1000 GMT 16 Jun 94 LD1606112994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] The Russian border guard has made a statement to China on its illegal actions during an incident on the Argun River in Amur Oblast. Chinese servicemen and Russian fishermen clashed on the border river on 12 June, and a Russian citizen was injured.
